query:
INSERT INTO
    ais_positions (
    mmsi,latitude,longitude,ais_message_type_id,timestamp,altitude,course_over_ground,navigation_status_id,ais_class,rate_of_turn,speed_over_ground,true_heading,distance_to_shore
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::INT[],$2::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$3::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$4::INT[],$5::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$6::INT[],$7::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$8::INT[],$9::TEXT[],$10::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$11::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$12::INT[],$13::DOUBLE PRECISION[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (mmsi,timestamp) DO NOTHING RETURNING mmsi AS "mmsi!:Mmsi",latitude AS "latitude!:f64",longitude AS "longitude!:f64",timestamp AS "timestamp!:DateTime<Utc>"
